DISPEL

Dispel (High Sorcery ability)

Usage:  dispel [target]
Cooldown:  9 seconds
Cost:  30 mana

This spell removes any magical or fire-based damage-over-time effects on the
target. The target must be affected by at least one such effect for this spell
to work.

