MIRRORIMAGE "MIRROR IMAGE"

Mirrorimage (High Sorcery ability)

Usage:  mirrorimage
Cooldown:  5 minutes
Cost:  20% of max mana

This spell creates an identical duplicate of the caster that deals no damage.
It's good enough to fool at least one of the people hitting you (they will
switch targets to the mirror image), and none of the people attacking you will
see the message that you split in two.

Mirror images are charmed, so they take orders. They can't be healed and will
only rescue you in combat one time. Once combat ends, they can't start combat
on their own, so they can't be re-used and are only useful when summoned in
combat. You can dismiss the mirror image and summon a new one.

Gain experience by summoning a mirror image.

See also: ORDER
