Ritual of Sense Life (High Sorcery skill)

Usage:  ritual senselife
Cost:  15 mana

This spell works similar to the "search ability" and can find people hidden
in the room with you, using simple magic. It also allows you to sense
earthmelded people.

Gains experience when you complete the ritual, whether or not you find
