SIPHON "MANA SIPHON"

Siphon (High Sorcery ability)

Usage:  siphon [victim]
Cooldown:  20 seconds
Duration:  20 seconds
Cost:  10 mana
Debuff type:  High Sorcery

You can steal mana from other casters using the mana siphon ability. If you are
in combat, it will automatically target your current opponent. This will boost
your own mana regen while dropping theirs significantly. The power of this spell
increases based on your High Sorcery level.

Obviously, this spell does not work on foes with no mana of their own.

Gain experience by casting this spell.
