SUNSHOCK "SUN SHOCK"

Sunshock (High Sorcery ability)

Usage:  sunshock [victim]
Cooldown:  9 seconds
Cost:  based on damage
Debuff type:  High Sorcery

Sunshock blasts your target with the pure light of the sun. This deals a small
amount of damage (scaled by your level, role, and traits), and causes a very
short blinding effect.

Sunshock does 1.5x damage to vampires, but this damage bonus does not change
the cost.

If you are in combat and specify no target, Sunshock hits your current
opponent.

Gains experience by casting this spell.

See also: BLIND
