THORNLASH "THORN LASH"

Thornlash
Class ability:  Theurge

Usage:  thornlash [victim]
Cooldown:  9 seconds
Cost:  based on damage
Debuff type:  High Sorcery

Thornlash wraps a coil of thorny vines around your victim. The vines cause
immediate pain, while the thorns dig in and deal poison damage over time. This
