VIGOR

Vigor (High Sorcery ability)

Usage:  vigor [target]
Cost:  15 / 25 / 40 mana
Debuff duration:  75 seconds

Your target receives a quick boost of movement points, at the cost of move
regeneration. Vigor cannot be recast on the same target until their move regen
recovers. The strength of this spell is based upon the caster's Intelligence
and High Sorcery level. 

The vigor bonus is doubled if the target is not in combat.

If your target is in combat, you will join the combat upon using this ability.

Vigor gains experience when you cast it.
